---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import { SITE } from '@lib/constants';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for Faithfully Crafted -- how we handle your data, third-party services, and your rights."
>
  <article class="py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-sm sm:prose-base">
      <header class="text-center mb-12" data-reveal="up">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-text">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-text-muted">Last updated: March 13, 2026</p>
      </header>

      <section data-reveal="up" data-reveal-delay="100">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">Introduction</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Faithfully Crafted ("we," "us," or "our") operates the website at
          <a href={SITE.url}>{SITE.url}</a>. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use,
          and protect information when you visit our website.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed mt-3">
          By using our website, you agree to the practices described in this policy. If you do not
          agree, please do not use the website.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section data-reveal="up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Our website is a static portfolio site. We do <strong class="text-text">not</strong> directly collect
          personal information from visitors. Specifically:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-text-muted mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li>We do not use contact forms that collect your name, email, or phone number on this site.</li>
          <li>We do not use cookies or tracking scripts originating from our website.</li>
          <li>We do not require account registration or login.</li>
          <li>All fonts are self-hosted on our servers -- no third-party font services track your visits.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section data-reveal="up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Our website relies on the following third-party services:
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-text mt-6 mb-2">Cloudflare</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Our website is hosted on Cloudflare Pages. Cloudflare may collect basic server logs
          (IP addresses, browser type, request timestamps) as part of standard web hosting
          operations. For details, see
          <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare's Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-text mt-6 mb-2">Facebook (Meta)</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Gallery content on this website is sourced from our public Facebook Page using the
          Facebook Graph API. This data is fetched at build time on our servers and served as
          static content -- no Facebook scripts, pixels, or tracking code runs in your browser
          when you visit our site. If you click links to our Facebook Page or Messenger, you
          will be subject to
          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/privacy/policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Meta's Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>

        <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold text-text mt-6 mb-2">Instagram (Meta)</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Our website contains links to our Instagram profile. No Instagram tracking code runs
          on our site. Clicking these links takes you to Instagram, which is governed by
          <a href="https://www.facebook.com/privacy/policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Meta's Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section data-reveal="up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">External Links</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Our website contains links to external websites and services (Facebook, Instagram,
          Messenger). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third-party sites.
          We encourage you to review their privacy policies before providing any personal
          information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section data-reveal="up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Our website is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly
          collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has provided us
          with personal information, please contact us so we can take appropriate action.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section data-reveal="up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">Data Security</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          We take reasonable measures to protect any information associated with our website.
          Our site is served over HTTPS with strict security headers, including Content Security
          Policy, HSTS, and X-Frame-Options.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section data-reveal="up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page
          with an updated "Last updated" date. Your continued use of the website after changes
          constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section data-reveal="up">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl font-bold text-text mt-10 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, you can reach us at:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-none text-text-muted mt-3 space-y-1">
          <li>Email: <a href={`mailto:${SITE.email}`}>{SITE.email}</a></li>
          <li>Facebook: <a href="https://www.facebook.com/gingerchets/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">facebook.com/gingerchets</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
